'we stayed in appts 20to 27 dec 11. note wasleft on agents window next to appts.to say where keys were.we knew name of hotel so didnt take long 10 mins each way main gate to apts was locked but a man let rest of our party wait inside till we got keys. appts basic but clean with plenty of towels.only downside was they were very cold at night only had one bar electric fire which we left on from t time onwards.other than that they were ok.'